OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury backs Pope
OL,4,Cafter scathing criticism from Donald
OL,5,CTrump
OL,7,FThe top bishop in the Church of
OL,8,FEngland has said she stands in
OL,9,Fsolidarity with the Pope's calls for
OL,10,Fpeace, amid a war of words which has
OL,11,Fbroken out between the pontiff and US
OL,12,Fpresident Donald Trump.
OL,14,FArchbishop of Canterbury Dame Sarah
OL,15,FMullally's backing for Pope Leo came
OL,16,Fas the head of the Catholic Church
OL,17,Fwarned on Thursday that the world is
OL,18,Fbeing "ravaged by a handful of
OL,19,Ftyrants".
OL,26,@zD@GOU{D@HO]
