OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776359147
OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury backs Pope
OL,4,Cafter scathing criticism from Donald
OL,5,CTrump
OL,7,FDame Sarah, who will meet the Pope
OL,8,Flater this month in Rome, said she
OL,9,Fstands with the pontiff "in his
OL,10,Fcourageous call for a kingdom of
OL,11,Fpeace" and urged "all those entrusted
OL,12,Fwith political authority to pursue
OL,13,Fevery possible peaceful and just means
OL,14,Fof resolving conflict".
OL,16,FEarlier this week, Mr Trump branded
OL,17,Fthe Pope "weak" and demanded the
OL,18,Freligious leader "focus on being a
OL,19,FGreat Pope, not a Politician".
