OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury backs Pope
OL,4,Cafter scathing criticism from Donald
OL,5,CTrump
OL,7,FThe comments were in stark contrast to
OL,8,Fhis remarks about the first US-born
OL,9,FPope on the day of the pontiff's
OL,11,Felection almost a year ago, which Mr
OL,12,FTrump had described as a "Great Honor
OL,13,Ffor our Country", and said he looked
OL,14,Fforward to meeting with the religious
OL,15,Fleader in what he predicted would be a
OL,16,F"very meaningful moment!"
OL,18,FThe US president this week told
OL,19,Freporters he did not think the pontiff
OL,20,Fwas "doing a very good job", adding
OL,21,Fthat he was "not a fan of Pope Leo".
