OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury backs Pope
OL,4,Cafter scathing criticism from Donald
OL,5,CTrump
OL,7,FThe scathing criticism from Mr Trump
OL,8,Ffollowed an Easter message earlier
OL,9,Fthis month in which the Pope strongly
OL,10,Fcriticised war, calling on "those who
OL,11,Fhave weapons (to) lay them down".
OL,13,FSince then, the Pope insisted he will
OL,14,Fcontinue to "stand up and say there's
OL,15,Fa better way" and that he is "not
OL,16,Fafraid of the Trump administration",
OL,17,Falthough he also said he did not
OL,18,Fintend to "get into a debate" with the
OL,19,FUS leader.
