OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury backs Pope
OL,4,Cafter scathing criticism from Donald
OL,5,CTrump
OL,7,FIn remarks on Thursday during his
OL,8,Fcurrent four-nation Africa tour, Pope
OL,9,FLeo remained outspoken in his
OL,10,Fcriticism of war and his want for
OL,11,Fpeace.
OL,13,FSpeaking at a cathedral in the western
OL,14,FCameroon city of Bamenda, he said:
OL,15,F"Blessed are the peacemakers.
OL,17,F"But woe to those who manipulate
OL,18,Freligion and the very name of God for
OL,19,Ftheir own military, economic and
OL,20,Fpolitical gain, dragging that which is
OL,21,Fsacred into darkness and filth."
OL,26,@wD@AOUyD@AOU
