OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury backs Pope
OL,4,Cafter scathing criticism from Donald
OL,5,CTrump
OL,7,FHe added: "The world is being ravaged
OL,8,Fby a handful of tyrants, yet it is
OL,9,Fheld together by a multitude of
OL,10,Fsupportive brothers and sisters."
OL,12,FIn a now-deleted post, Mr Trump had
OL,13,Fearlier this week, shared an image of
OL,14,Fhimself which many said appeared to be
OL,15,Fthe president as a Jesus-like figure.
OL,26,@oD@KOUrD@aO]
