OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury backs Pope
OL,4,Cafter scathing criticism from Donald
OL,5,CTrump
OL,7,FFollowing criticism from some, Mr
OL,8,FTrump rejected the idea he had likened
OL,9,Fhimself to the son of God, saying:
OL,10,F"It's supposed to be me as a doctor,
OL,11,Fmaking people better. And I do make
OL,12,Fpeople better. I make people a lot
OL,13,Fbetter."
OL,15,FDame Sarah said: "I stand with my
OL,16,Fbrother in Christ, His Holiness Pope
OL,17,FLeo XIV, in his courageous call for a
OL,18,Fkingdom of peace.
OL,26,@rD@AOUuD@HO]wD@ROU
