OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury backs Pope
OL,4,Cafter scathing criticism from Donald
OL,5,CTrump
OL,7,F"As innocent people are killed and
OL,8,Fdisplaced, families torn apart, and
OL,9,Ffutures destroyed, the human cost of
OL,10,Fwar is incalculable. It is the calling
OL,11,Fof every Christian ` and of all people
OL,12,Fof faith and goodwill ` to work and
OL,13,Fpray for peace.
OL,15,F"We must also urge all those entrusted
OL,16,Fwith political authority to pursue
OL,17,Fevery possible peaceful and just means
OL,18,Fof resolving conflict."
